      • createEnergyUnit

        public static EnergyUnits.EnergyUnit createEnergyUnit(java.lang.String unlocalizedName,
                                                      int multiplier,
                                                      int colour)
        Register an energy unit
        Parameters:
        unlocalizedName - The unlocalized name of the energy unit. You will need to add energy.unit.unlocalizedName.name and energy.unit.unlocalizedName.suffix to your language file
        multiplier - The multiplier to convert to the unit from MINECRAFT_JOULES 10RF = 1MJ 10FE = 1MJ 4J = 1MJ 6EU = 1MJ
        colour - The colour of the EnergyBar
        Returns:
        The registered energy unit
